      "text": "Bet DEews nahze pee Abi-\nmeleku Sapni Nakti / un fazzija\nus to: Redstew irr ja-mirst tahs\nSeewas deht / ko tu efi nehmis/\njo ta irr weena lanata Seewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Abimeleks winnu wehl\nne bij aiskahris / tad fazzija tas:\nKUNGS / arri tu taifnus Lau-\ndis nonahweti ?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi tas pats us man faz-\nzijis : ta irr manna Mahfa / un\nwinna patti arridsan irr fazzijusi/\ntas irr mans Brahlis: Es esmu\nto no mannas Sir̄ds Weenteesti-\nbas/un no manno Rohku Schih-\nstivas darrijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Deews us to/\nSapni: Es finnu arridsan/ ka tu\nfcho no tawas Sir̄ds Weenteefi-\nbas efi darrijis / un es esmu tew\narridsan aiskawejis / ka tu prett\nmann ne grehkotn/ tadeht es tew\nne esmu patahwis winnu ais-\nkahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nu/ atdoht tam Wihran\nto Seewu / jo tas irr weens Bra-\nweets/ un lai wiꞥsch preeksch teiw\nInhds/ tad tu dsihwofi / bet ja tu\nto ne atdohti / tad finni / ka tu\nmirdains mirsi/ un wiſs/ kas tew\npeederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks zehlehs agri/\nun aizinaja wiſs sawus Kal-\npus / un runnaja wiſs schohs\nWahrdus preeksch winzo Ausim/\nun tee Wihti bibijajhs tohti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks aizinaja to Ab-\nbrāimu/ un fazzija us to: Kami\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks fazzija uē\nAbbrāimu / ko efi tu redsejis/ ka\ntu to efi darrijis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ahbrāims: Ge-\ndohmaju/ kas finna/ Deewa Bih-\njaschana ne irr schinni Weetā/ un\ntee nokaus manu mannas See-\nwas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un taifrsan teefcham\nmanns Mahfa/ manna Tehwa\nMeita / bet ne mannas Mahte-\nMeita / un ta irr manna Seewa\ntapputi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz to/ kad DEews\nman no manna Tehwa Namma\nlizzis bohkfriters / tad fazztju ce\nus to: Lai fchi irr ta Schehlasti-\nba / ko tu pee man darrijis: Wis-\nfur / furp mehs nahftin / fatt-\nno mannim/ tas irr mans Brah-\nlis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Abimeleks\nAwis/un Wehrfchus/un Kalpus,\nun Kalpones / un dewe tohs Ah-\nbrāinam / un atdewe tam Sar-\nmirdains mirsi/ un wiſs/ kas tew\nfawn Seewu arridsan.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks fazzija\nRaugi/ manna Semme irr taw-\nPreekfchā / dsihwo / kur tas ta-\nwahm Azzim lab patihk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un uhs Saru fazzija\nwiꞥsch : Reds / es eftmu tawam\nBrahtam tuhkfsochus Sudrabe-\nGabbalus dewis / un redsi la-\nta\n"
    }
